package main

			Name:        pulumi.String("test-project"),
			RecipeName:  pulumi.String("test-project-recipe"),

				Type: "LAST_N",
			},
			Tags: []databrew.ProjectTagArgs{
				&databrew.ProjectTagArgs{

					Value: pulumi.String("value001AtCreate"),
				},

		}

}
